# Goal: deliver the currently-held tool to a receiver hand.
# If hand_pose.header.frame_id is empty, the executor waits for the
# surgeon's double_open_close gesture and then uses the last /hand_state.
# If hand_pose.header.frame_id is set, that pose is used directly (no
# gesture wait — manual / test bypass).
geometry_msgs/PoseStamped hand_pose
---
# Result
bool success
string message
---
# Feedback
string phase         # AWAITING_GESTURE | MOVING_TO_HAND | RELEASED
